data.description: This 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home is truly one-of-a-kind! You must tour the primary suite to appreciate everything it has to offer. The bathroom features a steam shower, Mahogany French doors, heated floors, a heated towel rack, and an oversized soaking tub with a vanishing TV in the mirror. You can relax by the fireplace, enjoy the wet bar, or the private deck. The wood floors are African Sapele. There is also a second primary suite across the house perfect for any guest or family member. This ranch home is controlled by a newer 3-zone hi-efficiency hot water heating system. The oversized living room has a beautiful view of Lake Vermilion across the street. The kitchen features an ample amount of cabinets, an island, and stainless steel appliances. This home sits on 1.04 acres and has so much to offer the next homeowner. Call today to tour this gorgeous property!
